-deeds-al-sayyiat","tag-fasting-al-siyam","tag-hypocrisy-al-nifaq","tag-intention-al-niyyah","tag-manners-adab","tag-negligence-al-ghaflah","tag-night-prayer-al-tahajjud","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-sincerity-al-ikhlas","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-54m","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/acts-of-worship-spoiled\/","url_meta":{"origin":19490,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Worship: Acts of worship spoiled by insincerity and sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne who fasts might only acquire hunger and thirst from his fasting. One who stands for prayer might only acquire fatigue from his prayer.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 13413 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/18\/siyam-salat-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":19490,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Reward of fasting and praying in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts the month of Ramadan due to faith and seeking reward, his previous sins will be forgiven. Whoever stands in prayer during the Night of Decree due to faith and seeking reward, his previous sins\u2026",